{"tid":2097221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柏良指政府沒有認真處理檢疫措施漏洞 相信零星個案陸續有來","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T21:59:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6a8f4ba7a35018a230adb1fcc484a41c98d20b","tid":2097221,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良指, 本港再出現新型肺炎本地確診個案, 屬預期之內, 反映政府沒有認真處理檢疫措施漏洞, 沒有決心做, 相信零星個案可能陸續有來.<br />\n        何柏良在電台節目中說, 昨日的一宗新增本地個案的感染源頭未明, 患者分別在坪石邨及屯門內河碼頭兩間食肆工作, 估計一定有群組爆發風險, 食肆員工及食客或有機會中招. 他建議當局參考內地, 及外國設街站收集樣本化驗, 他認為這個做法不構成傳染風險.<br />\n        何柏良又指, 當局最好的策略是做好源頭管理, 建議在11個高危行業, 包括飲食、 酒吧、 健身和美容業等. 設定病毒檢測機制, 盡量便利他們接受檢測, 及早發現潛在確診個案.<br />\n        <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200706112634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200706112634&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=53693e1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200706112634</a>"},{"pid":"d085fc877bd191401fca02b66bc97a56b00871e1","tid":2097221,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:37:25.000Z","msg":"何柏良違反蟈安法，拉得"},{"pid":"50f692e2ac9e17b8855ddc5194acb937d062b5bf","tid":2097221,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"何柏良<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d902d35bc4cf08e65c05ecad936892caf331f7f","tid":2097221,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"我哋政府係咩都唔做,<br />\n吹咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485f37b52d42e0c09f606dbb6d51c00a1586a492","tid":2097221,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50f692e2ac9e17b8855ddc5194acb937d062b5bf","tid":2097221,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T1